            </div>
            <div type="commentary"> 
                <list type="witDetail">
                    <item n="1"><p>Although there are a few examples of the name Ruarc(c) in the <ref target="https://celt.ucc.ie/published/T100001A/index.html">Annals of Ulster</ref> from the ninth and tenth centuies, I don't know of any other example of Ruarcán, with the diminutive suffix.</p></item>
